{"tid":616440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"YouTube總部槍擊案　槍手是活躍用戶　曾怨「30萬瀏覽人次獲利僅0.1美元」","createTime":"2018-04-04T07:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T09:50:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b5fca9124f063948677af560dd8e8e90c1c13da5","tid":616440,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180404/s00005/990678c0e00d4ed8056dfbff5d861b6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180404%2Fs00005%2F990678c0e00d4ed8056dfbff5d861b6b.jpg&h=b785743a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180404/s00005/98e293f8f9e6111d0f0a5623d11477eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180404%2Fs00005%2F98e293f8f9e6111d0f0a5623d11477eb.jpg&h=98dd4253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國加州聖布魯諾市YouTube總部，周二（3日）發生槍擊事件，至少3人受傷，女槍手開槍自盡。根據全國廣播公司偵查所得，槍手是39歲阿格達姆（Nasim Aghdam）。<br />\n<br />\n據報阿格達姆自稱健美運動員，祖籍不明，但懂得說波斯語。她是Youtube活躍用戶，經常上載健身短片，又不時批評YouTube審查制度。<br />\n<br />\n去年1月，阿格達姆在一段短片中，斥Youtube對其健身短片施加年齡限制，並表示與明星片段相比，Youtube對她片段的限制，明顯帶有雙重標準。<br />\n<br />\n她亦曾在個人網站聲稱受到YouTube不斷打壓，「30萬瀏覽人次僅獲利0.1美元」；引用二戰納粹德國領袖希特拉名言，「誇大一個謊言，簡化一個謊言，不斷說一個謊言，人們最後便會相信這個謊言」，質疑現時西方國家是否仍然有言論自由。除此之外，她指自己是素食主義者，批評美軍使用豬隻作訓練用途，並在社交網站上載圖片，指「食肉等同謀殺」。<br />\n<br />\n她的頻道「Nasime Sabz」有超過1.2萬名訂閱者，但已因「屢次或嚴重違反 YouTube禁止垃圾內容、詐欺行為及誤導性內容的政策或其他《服務條款》」而停權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180404/s00005/1522822926765\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180404%2Fs00005%2F1522822926765&d=EQeDkbj5XTFf33Q5RgtclcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=8f948d84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180404%2Fs00005%2F1522822926765&h=82d1db81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180404/s00005/1522822926765</a>"},{"pid":"176f9f7b3b2de57fc96ee3a1757088180e59d89f","tid":616440,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:03:08.000Z","msg":"呢條女個channel好柒恐怖咁下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb1ea7a91f9bbff8ba862b1a9a0e514b4a45906","tid":616440,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:07:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b1Vi4YGMGkk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db1Vi4YGMGkk&d=EQeDkbj5XTFf33Q5RgtclcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=9c3934a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b1Vi4YGMGkk</a><br />\n<br />\n好似D神秘影片咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f7283b457c91eca704a5bf1637c27f0d8eeedb","tid":616440,"uid":83623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:07:30.000Z","msg":"算唔算第一單因為demonetized反擊YouTube <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c46f2a38b2d7c1933087ecfcbef97d426152f9","tid":616440,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:10:06.000Z","msg":"39歲算keep得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcddf73d2a8ab2bf6f53e211cb6ce8a1c5ea0e7c","tid":616440,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:12:00.000Z","msg":"質疑現時西方國家是否仍然有言論自由<br />\n<br />\n左膠橫行下一早無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f6d8208b735d445f4f96ca7f8b4ced623904ac","tid":616440